    <div class="a-c">
      <p>Haven is a simple web app for helping you get started with meditation.</p>
      <p>If that sounds strange or foreign to you, don&rsquo;t worry! Meditation is simply about taking time for yourself and giving yourself permission to be still, calm, and thoughtfully focused.</p>
      <p>Of course, meditation <em>can</em> involve mantras, yoga poses, and so on, but this app focuses on simpler, more accessible meditation. If you&rsquo;re like most people, you could use a little more clarity and focus in your life, so take 5 minutes and let Haven guide you through a simple meditation session. It&rsquo;s one of the simplest things you can do to improve your mental health.</p>
    </div>

